@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_trkhrz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(0.41)
    v0 = ((v2 / wp.cos(v0 + 0.45)) * wp.cos(tmp))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.05)))
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v0 + 0.52) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.18)))
    v0 = wp.sin((tmp / (tmp + 0.28 / v2 + 0.46)))
    data[tid] = v0
